istance.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Steyn\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 636}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"a time of2:32:51\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 673}, {\"ngram\": \"her South African record\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From early on in the race, those following closely on television would have noticed that the 34-year-old was conspicuous by her absence among the lead runners.\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"her absence\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead runners\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Post-race, Gerda Steyntook to social mediato explain that she did not have her best day out on the roads of the French capital.\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8659230565373167, \"rank\": 0.15256642445257662, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Post\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"Gerda Steyntook\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"social mediato\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"her best day\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the roads\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Wow, what an experience!!!\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Wow, what an experience\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(but I am really glad it's over) \\ud83e\\udd23The crowds were unbelievable and I will never forget this experience everrrr!!\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1163, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\ud83e\\udd23\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"The crowds\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you to those who have literally showered me with support and even though I did not run in the way I feel I am capable of, or trained for, I am still really proud to be part of this and I hope that my results today will also be a reminder to always keep going, even when the going gets tough \\ud83d\\udcaa\\ud83c\\udffe\\ud83d\\udcaa\\ud83c\\udffeI did not feel good from the start and knew early on that it would be a tough day out, but I never thought about giving up because of all of YOU \\ud83e\\udef5\\ud83c\\udffd who always cheer me on and believe in me, no matter what challenge I take on!I am living my dream life and today's results will not change any of that!!\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1342}, {\"ngram\": \"my results\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"a reminder\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the going\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"tough \\ud83d\\udcaa\\ud83c\\udffe\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"\\ud83d\\udcaa\\ud83c\\udffeI\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough day\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"\\ud83e\\udef5\\ud83c\\udffd\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"what challenge\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"my dream life\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"today's results\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"!\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9bCongratulations to@cianol